Detailed Description

template<class TYPE>
class StatWithRatesOfChange< TYPE >

This class is used to keep a statistic.

The rate of change of this statistic is monitored.

template<class TYPE>
void StatWithRatesOfChange< TYPE >::monitorRateOfChange ( float  numSamples  )  [inline]

This method is used to start the monitoring of the rate of change of this stat.

It does this using an Exponential Moving Average. This is set up so that the most recent "numSamples" samples makes up "weighting" of the result.
